results.wikipedia_summary: Aethopyga is a genus of birds in the Nectariniidae family. Species in this genus are found in South Asia, Southeast Asia and parts of China. Many species such as the Grey-hooded Sunbird, Mount Apo Sunbird, Metallic-winged Sunbird, Handsome Sunbird and Lina's Sunbird are endemic to the Philippines.
